      • canCatchFire

        public boolean canCatchFire(IBlockAccess world,
                   BlockPos pos,
                   EnumFacing face)
        Side sensitive version that calls the block function.
        Parameters:
        world - The current world
        pos - Block position
        face - The side the fire is coming from
